{
  "stem": "11641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here, you know, the German masters, they were hitting-- if they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had full power of life and death, if they wanted to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I spoke German, so I didn't-- more or less, you had to play by ear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of them, yeah, at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was never adequate food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They gave you soup and a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- it was-- was sort of not enough to live, and too much to die-- type of thing-- in the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the concentration camp, it was different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody close, really, I could consider friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "More or less, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother was working, as I told you, for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father and my uncle, my aunt's husband, they were both doing these things with the wood.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were managing in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there always a constant fear of-- of killing, because they were like an open season over there, in the ghetto B.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not disappearing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would kill people on the outside of the ghetto that were caught without passes, without-- they say, oh, they caught some Jewish girls who somebody pointed at them, that they were Jewish-- Jewesses.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They killed them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was sent to Plaszow, things were entirely different.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, you were surrounded by barbed wire, all around you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't get out of there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- you were part of a barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the barrack was called Bochnia Barrack, because all those who was caught there-- there was from Bochnia ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- And you were under strict orders, working area, where you got up 6 o'clock in the morning and you worked until dusk.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
